### 3.4 JWT Token Structure\
\
```json\
\{\
  "sub": "usr_01HXYZ...",\
  "email": "john@horizonflights.com",\
  "tenant_id": "org_01HABC...",\
  "roles": ["owner"],\
  "permissions": ["aircraft:write", "users:invite", "logbook:sign"],\
  "iat": 1711900000,\
  "exp": 1711986400\
\}\
```\
\
All API calls carry this JWT. Every database query automatically filters by `tenant_id` using **Row-Level Security (RLS)** \'97 no cross-tenant data leakage is possible at DB level.\
