## 8. Logbooks & Document Management\
\
### 8.1 Logbook Types\
\
| Logbook | What It Tracks |\
|---------|----------------|\
| **Airframe Logbook** | Airframe inspections, repairs, alterations, annual inspections |\
| **Engine Logbook(s)** | Per-engine maintenance, overhauls, cylinder work, TSMOH |\
| **Propeller Logbook(s)** | Prop maintenance, overhauls, strikes |\
| **Component Logbook** | Life-limited parts, avionics LRUs, mods |\
| **Mechanic's Personal Log** | Mechanic's own work record (separate from aircraft logs) |\
\
