### 8.5 Book Visibility Control (Owner sets per mechanic)\
\
When an owner invites a mechanic or edits their access, they specify exactly which logbooks that mechanic can see:\
\
```\
For mechanic mike@airmech.com on aircraft N1234X:\
  Airframe Logbook:      \uc0\u9989  READ + WRITE\
  Engine 1 Logbook:      \uc0\u9989  READ + WRITE\
  Engine 2 Logbook:      \uc0\u10060  NO ACCESS\
  Propeller Logbook:     \uc0\u9989  READ ONLY\
  Component Logbook:     \uc0\u10060  NO ACCESS\
  AD Compliance:         \uc0\u9989  READ ONLY\
```\
\
This is stored as a JSON permissions map in `aircraft_access.book_permissions` and enforced server-side on every API call.\
\
