## 9. Permission & Access Control Matrix\
\
### 9.1 Permission Resolution Order\
\
```\
1. Check user is authenticated (JWT valid, not expired)\
2. Check tenant_id matches resource tenant (RLS)\
3. Check user's org-level role\
4. Check user's aircraft-level access record\
5. Check user's book-level permission within that aircraft access\
6. Allow or deny\
```\
\
