## 14. State Machines\
\
### 14.1 Aircraft Access State Machine\
\
```\
               grant_access()\
[NO_ACCESS] \uc0\u9472 \u9472 \u9472 \u9472 \u9472 \u9472 \u9472 \u9472 \u9472 \u9472 \u9472 \u9472 \u9472 \u9472 \u9472 \u9472 \u9472 \u9658  [ACTIVE]\
                                   \uc0\u9474 \
                    \uc0\u9484 \u9472 \u9472 \u9472 \u9472 \u9472 \u9472 \u9472 \u9472 \u9472 \u9472 \u9472 \u9472 \u9472 \u9472 \u9532 \u9472 \u9472 \u9472 \u9472 \u9472 \u9472 \u9472 \u9472 \u9472 \u9472 \u9472 \u9472 \u9472 \u9472 \u9488 \
                    \uc0\u9474               \u9474                \u9474 \
              revoke()      expires_at           update()\
              by owner      passes               by owner\
                    \uc0\u9474               \u9474                \u9474 \
                    \uc0\u9660               \u9660                \u9474 \
               [REVOKED]      [EXPIRED]    [ACTIVE] (updated)\
                    \uc0\u9474 \
             re_grant() if owner chooses\
                    \uc0\u9474 \
                    \uc0\u9660 \
                [ACTIVE]\
```\
\
