### 14.3 User Role Transition Rules\
\
```\
Role changes can ONLY be made by:\
  - Owner: can promote anyone, can demote anyone except themselves\
  - Owner-Admin: can promote up to Owner-Admin, cannot demote Owner\
  - A&P Mechanic: can only manage their own sub-users (AMP/OJT)\
\
Role change requires audit log entry:\
\{\
  action: "role_changed",\
  changed_by: user_id,\
  target_user: user_id,\
  from_role: "ojt",\
  to_role: "amp",\
  aircraft_scope: ["acft_01HXK9"]\
\}\
```\
